{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/extras/EndlessNight_Title_Logo_2024_V6.png?t=1736802191\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Until you make the unconscious conscious, <strong>it will direct your life and you will call it fate</strong>&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 -Carl G. Jung</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jake\u2019s journey begins where most fear to tread\u2014deep within the shadows of his own mind. Guided only by fragments of memory and a will to survive, he must confront the darkness that threatens to consume him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What awaits in the depths? Fear, doubt, and pain\u2026 or the strength to overcome it all? The choice is yours: confront the darkness\u2014or let it define you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/extras/ekaj-optimize.gif?t=1736802191\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNIQUE PLATFORMING MECHANICS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a platforming experience like no other, featuring fireflies with extraordinary abilities such as horizontal and vertical boosts, teleportation, and gravity manipulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/extras/fireflies_misc-optimize.gif?t=1736802191\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ENGAGING COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face a variety of enemies, each with complex attack patterns and tactical challenges. Adapt your fighting style to overcome increasingly difficult foes as your character evolves, unlocks new moves, and gets more powerful gear that alters his combat characteristics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/extras/spiders-optimize.gif?t=1736802191\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STUNNING ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in the captivating world of <i>Endless Night: The Darkness Within</i>, featuring breathtaking visuals and plenty of mysteries to uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/extras/vigil_walkthrough-optimize.gif?t=1736802191\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHARACTER CUSTOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tailor your character to suit your play style with a wide range of dope gear. Mix and match gear to enhance your abilities and create powerful combinations, which you will need, because we all know that it's dangerous to go alone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/extras/equipment-crop.gif?t=1736802191\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736802191","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/page.bg.jpg?t=1736802191","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/2b0b665ecb7c9cdf651bfbae600629c23ea6c9da/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736802191","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533140/2b0b665ecb7c9cd